OL,7,FAn infected blood scandal campaigner
OL,8,Ffrom says victims like her still
OL,9,Fhaven't had the time to heal.
OL,11,FNow they have even more uncertainty
OL,12,Fafter the public inquiry report was
OL,13,Fpublished.
OL,15,FRos Cooper from Bewdley was infected
OL,16,Fwith hepatitis C as a child while
OL,17,Freceiving treatment for a blood
OL,18,Fdisorder.
