OL,5,Cpayments
OL,7,FShe long campaigned for compensation,
OL,8,Fwhich the Government announced will be
OL,9,Fpaid.
OL,11,FBut Ros and other victims have since
OL,12,Ffound out that could replace the
OL,13,Fsupport payments they've long relied
OL,14,Fon - as a result of the health scandal
OL,15,Fthat left many unable to work.
OL,17,FRos found out those blood products had
OL,18,Finfected her with hepatitis C aged 19
OL,19,Fbut doesn't know when exactly she was
OL,20,Finfected as her medical notes have
OL,21,Fbeen lost.
