OL,7,FYet through all this, .
OL,9,FAfter a six-year inquiry, Prime
OL,10,FMinister Rishi Sunak made a public
OL,11,Fapology to those affected by the
OL,12,Fcontaminated blood scandal.
OL,14,FRos had to give up work after years of
OL,15,Fnasty side effects from hepatitis c
OL,16,Ftreatment and so the support payments
OL,17,Fbecame a lifeline.
