OL,7,FBut it's not just about the money -
OL,8,Fshe says the Government have yet to
OL,9,Fprovide any psychological support or
OL,10,Ftherapy for victims.
OL,12,FThe Infected Blood Compensation Scheme
OL,13,Fis due to replace any previous support
OL,14,Fpayments to victims by April next year.
OL,16,FIn the Commons, Minister for the
OL,17,FCabinet Office, John Glen said: "We
OL,18,Fwill ensure that no-one receives less
OL,19,Fin compensation than they would have
OL,20,Freceived in support payments.
