OL,7,FThe legislation to compensate the
OL,8,Fvictims was one of the last to be
OL,9,Fpassed before Parliament was dissolved
OL,10,Ffor the General Election. And with
OL,11,Fcross-party consensus - both Labour
OL,12,Fand the Conservatives have committed
OL,13,Fto compensating the victims.
